<!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
<section class="section about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
  
    <div class="header">
      <h1 class="header-text">National Bail Bond Surety Managing General Agency</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="fancy-header">       
      <h1>Forty years of experience supporting and serving the nation's professional bail agents</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span12">
        <div class="tabset">
          <ul class="tabs styled-list">
            <li class="tab tab-left"><a href="#panel1" class="selected">Who We Are</a></li>
            <li class="tab"><a href="#panel2" class="">From the President</a></li>
            <li class="tab"><a href="#panel3" class="">Why Choose Us?</a></li>
            <li class="tab"><a href="#panel4" class="">About Poindexter</a></li>
            <li class="tab tab-right"><a href="#panel5" class="">Philanthropy</a></li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="panel" id="panel1">
          	<h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>Poindexter Surety Services is a bail bond general agency/managing general agency and member of the Poindexter Surety Group of Companies.  Poindexter Surety is headquartered in Raleigh, North Carolina, with regional representatives and subagencies in over twenty states.  We were established in the year 2000 as a subsidiary of Poindexter &amp; Associates, Inc., a North Carolina coporation.  The spin-off was accomplished to allow Poindexter &amp; Associates, Inc., to return to its core business as declared in its charter.  <a href="http://www.poindexter-associates.com" target="_blank">Poindexter &amp; Associates, Inc.</a>, continues to provide insurance fraud investigation and loss runoff operations independently of Poindexter Surety, and offering skip trace and fugitive recovery support to Poindexter Surety bail agent partners.</p>
            <p>
            Our company principal is dedicated to the continued growth and stability of the private bail profession.  For that reason Poindexter Surety supports the efforts of the following professional bail agent associations:<br /><br />
            Professional Bail Agents Association of the U.S (P.B.U.S.) [<a href="docs/professional-bail-agents-of-the-us-membership.pdf" target="_blank">Membership Certificate</a>]<br />
            Professional Bondsmen of Texas (P.B.T.) [<a href="docs/professional-bondsmen-of-texas-membership_2017.pdf" target="_blank">Membership Certificate</a>]<br />
            North Carolina Bail Agents Association (N.C.B.A.A.) [<a href="docs/nc-bail-agents-association-membership.pdf" target="_blank">Membership Certificate</a>]<br />
            Tennessee Bail Agents Association (T.A.P.B.A.)<br />
            Association of Louisiana Bail Underwriters (A.L.B.U.)<br />
            Florida Surety Agents Association. (F.S.A.A.)<br />
            California Bail Agents Association (C.B.A.A.)<br />
            South Carolina Bail Agents Association (S.C.B.A.A.)<br />
            Professional Bail Agents of Idaho (P.B.A.I.)<br />
            Washington State Bail Agents Association (W.S.B.A.A.)<br />
            Ohio Bail Agents Association (O.B.A.A.) [<a href="docs/ohio-bail-agents-association-membership.pdf" target="_blank">Membership Certificate</a>]
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="panel" id="panel2">
            <h2>From The President</h2>
            <p>Never in the history of private, commerical bail have we faced a more difficult market. Encroachment by pretrial release services, governemnt sponsored monitoring programs, and oversaturation of bail agents in many areas are but a few of the challenges with which we must contend in our chosen field. I feel that having an appropriate surety partner is vital to your success in the bail bond profession. Like my peers I provide agency contracts, powers of attorney, seals, and other basics. Big deal, right? I agree! So, why partner with me? Consider these qualities:</p>
            <div class="pd"><img src="images/pd.jpg" alt="C. Poindexter"></div>
            <p class="qualities">
              <span><img src="images/qualities.png" /> &nbsp; Integrity, Tansparency, and truthful responses</span>
              <span><img src="images/qualities.png" /> &nbsp; Knowledge gained through experience</span>
              <span><img src="images/qualities.png" /> &nbsp; Personal and immediate attention</span>
              <span><img src="images/qualities.png" /> &nbsp; Strong, solvent carriers</span>
              <span><img src="images/qualities.png" /> &nbsp; Understanding</span>
            </p>
            <p>As a new retail bail agent many years ago, these are qualities that I would like to have found in my surety. Many times I did not. As I grew in the bail bond business and began to partner with a significant number of producers, I thought about my past experiences. I spent a great deal of time thinking about what caused me pain, and more importantly, how to keep my associates from suffering the same. The previous five qualities represent the actions that I took to prevent <u>you</u> from going through what I did.</p><br />
            <p>If these qualities are important to you, I invite you to apply for an agency relationship with Poindexter Surety Services. I sincerely believe that you will find our level of dedication to your success UNEQUALED! I hope to hear from you.</p>
            <p>C. Poindexter</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="panel" id="panel3">
          	<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>Wow! This is a simple one! We love writing bonds! More specifically we love helping people be successful in this profession because we are going to reach our goals, by helping you reach YOURS! What else? How about integrity and transparency, . . . doing what we promise to do, . . . being attentive to your needs, requests and long term strategy, . . . in general, being a knowledgeable, solid bail service and support organization. We are truly dedicated to you. We offer a fair operating agreement and a true friendship to our bail agent partners. Although we have been doing this since 1993, we look forwarding to partnering with you as we also continue to learn and grow.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="panel" id="panel4">
          	<h2>ABOUT POINDEXTER</h2>
            <p>Poindexter Surety Services is a member of The Poindexter Group of Companies, focused exclusively on the commercial bail surety market within the United States, Puerto Rico, U.S. Virgin Islands, and U.S. Territories. Poindexter Surety has been serving the underwriting needs of professional bail agents across the United States since 1995. Our goal is to provide superlative support and service to our bail agencies. We strive to be the independent bail agent's partner of choice, offering innovative, industry-leading solutions and our industry-specific knowlege to each bail agent. We diligently collaborate with each agent to build his or her respective book of business, then support his or her ongoing profitablity.</p>
            <p>Part of our value proposition is our stability. Diversification being key to 'weathering' sudden economic changes, The Poindexter Group of Companies offers a broad variety of legal and quasi-legal services:</p>
            <p>
            <strong>Surety One, Inc.</strong> - National surety and fidelity bond underwriter<br />
            <strong>Poindexter &amp; Associates, Inc.</strong> - Multi-state licensed investigative agency<br />
            <strong>Janus Assurance Re</strong> - Poindexter captive insurance compay<br />
            <strong>Arkansas Surety Corporation</strong> - Arkansas-focused bonding operations<br />
            <strong>Def-Tech, Ltd.</strong> - Department of Defense contracting organization<br />
            <strong>Judicial Process of North Carolina</strong> - Private constabulary service<br />
            <strong>Villar . S&aacute;nchez . Poindexter, Consultores Legales, S.A.</strong> - Law firm
            <p>
						<p>Poindexter Surety Services and its company principal/compliance agent are licensed property/casualty/surety producers and/or licensed bail agent/general agent for bail, in all fifty states, Puerto Rico, U.S. Virgin Islands, and Guam. Where statutorily required, Poindexter Surety Services also holds corporate certificates of authority.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="panel" id="panel5">
          	<h2>Philanthropy</h2>
            <p>We the team members of Surety One, Inc. take very seriously our responsibility to contribute to the relief of the sick, disabled, and less fortunate members of our communities. We give as liberally as possible to legitimate medical research foundations and philanthropic groups on a monthly disbursement basis.</p>
						<p>Nosotros, tomamos muy en serio nuestra responsabilidad social y mas especialmente hacía las personas y comunidades desfavorecidas de nuestro país. Cada mes donamos fondos tan libremente como nos es posible a grupos nacionales e internacionales ben&eacute;ficos y caritativos, tambi&eacute;n a fundaciones m&eacute;dicas de investigaci&oacute;n y desarrollo.</p>
